Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.25,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让机会溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.40,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的自由被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:48.33,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,叛逆的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:53.03,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来自我需跨越的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.36,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有的付出皆非徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.45,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽欲望 难以自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.90,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,理想与现实这般痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.27,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种方法改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:06.88,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.24,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是重点 谁会在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.27,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,绘画不好 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:17.00,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,让我仅为唯一的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.73,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,克服自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.10,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一个只有神知道的崭新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.28,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你内心的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.91,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,成为骑士为你照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:28.08,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.04,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不再害怕 不再流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.72,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会迎刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.73,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这是“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.73,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不要误解我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.28,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:44.54,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,但我会为你做一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.37,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我的生活发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.18,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,翻过这一页来到一个新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:48.03,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 没有人可以审判我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:48.02,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,每个结局指向下一阶段的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.89,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,尝试让我的人生完整 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.47,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要坚强 尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:02:02.72,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不要回头 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:01.15,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,活出自己 要快乐 这是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:06.21,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为你的人生找到真爱和归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.25,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.40,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:48.33,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Reason as against motion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:53.03,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.36,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.45,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Endless desire, like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.90,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pain, the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.27,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:06.88,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.24,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if sing off-key, who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.27,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good at drawing, no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:17.00,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.10,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole new world god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.28,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you’re hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.91,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a knight to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:28.08,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.04,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,No more fears No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.72,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s “god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.28,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,This in not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:44.54,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.37,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:48.03,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.18,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:48.02,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.89,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to make my life complete, trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.47,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:02:02.72,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look back, carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:01.15,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Be yourself be happy it's your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:06.21,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Find your love find your way for your life
